Text: Revised Customer Listpst Attached is the revised list with changes you requested I spoke with Frank Vickers about a few of the entries to ensure they were not duplicates with regards to Cities and their departs He advised that we would consider them two customers Example Talahassee City of Talahassee Electric Gas Department Franks group is working on a second generation list which would have the first column represent the Holding Co and the next column the subsidiary this would greatly assist with sorting the information After your review I can send back to the gas teams and ask them to populate some of the missing data if you wish Regards Tammy

Gas customerspst Louise Attached is the customer list Enovate and MW gas both roll into Laura Luce do you wish to treat them as separate regions In the mean time Ill begin working through the changes you requested Tammy

th floor Cc Attached are the seating assignments for the th floor of the new building provided to me by Ina Rangel Will you kindly review the list and compare to the names you provided so we can develop a list for Sally of who will need to be seated on the th floor Thanks Tammy

Board slidesBen Version includes alot of data that wasnt used but you might find interesting It was gathered from a number of parties Version B is the last version I have if Corp made changes I dont have them As you know the generation slide slide contains sensitive information so please dont forward the file or if you do simple delete it from the presentation Thanks again for your help Tammy Benjamin Rogers AM To Tammy R CT cc Subject Tammy I wanted to see if I could get a couple of the board presentation that you were working on with regards to the generation information I wanted to see how it turned out Thanks Ben

First Turbine Position Reportis the turbine report we discussed yesterday We will continue to prepare the LM list you have seen in the past but this will replace the master turbine list and will be updated biweekly Regards Tammy Forwarded by Tammy R ShepperdHOUECT on AM From Stephanie McGinnis PM To Rick CT Chip nron Rick L CT Steve W CT Rob CT John CT Richard CT Jody CT Tammy R CT Brian D BartoENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT John GarrisonENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Fred L KellyENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT John G RigbyENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT Dick WestfahlENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT cc Subject First Turbine Position Report Attached is our first Turbine Position Report We intend to issue this report every other Friday going forward This report contains a detail report by turbine as well as three summary reports Summary by Status Summary by Controlling Region Summary by Turbine Type Some of the financial data in this report is preliminary I will be working with the respective regional accounting groups to establish procedures for financial updates on a regular basis In the meantime I welcome any corrections suggestions you may have Thank you Stephanie
